{"tid":938217,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"祖母誤信偏方灑花椒粉止血 累9歲孫女夾傷變截肢","createTime":"2018-12-12T06:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T07:25:22.000Z","uid":75969,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"efa64ee8b2073b1128a62559c9ce4fed40e9cba5","tid":938217,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181211/_2018121120084950283.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181211%2F_2018121120084950283.jpg&h=00614457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑龍江大慶一名9歲女孩被家中防盜門夾傷手指，女童祖母見狀，竟然採取「民間療法」，將花椒粉撒在傷口想止血；豈料造成女童二次傷害，傷口被花椒粉感染，本來僅需將手指末端截肢，現在則必須把手指中段以上整個切除。<br />\n<br />\n女童父親表示，家中防盜門很重，加上事發當天風大，女童走路又慢，強風颳來導致門夾傷女童的手。祖母看見孫女受傷，慌忙中決定採用偏方，將花椒粉撒在傷口上，成功將血止住；然而女童治理後，醫生坦言只需從末端截肢的手指，由於傷口被花椒粉感染，不得不從中部截肢。<br />\n<br />\n事件曝光後，内地大批網民感嘆「信偏方害人不淺」，表示「無知真可怕」、「心疼小姑娘，本來去趟醫院就能解決的事」、「千萬別信偏方」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/885580\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F885580&d=3LHRZsUT7ChIVUMdJzdItxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=51a73f4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F885580&h=2a07a0c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/885580</a><br />\n<br />\n家有一老如有一寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2c4f278c5c3cf02967524afc45094b0700c243","tid":938217,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:45:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0499478391134d224a1a502c7f410fda07893dbe","tid":938217,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike"